{"tid":1277890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做實事既人入黎] 鳩post收皮，實幹post整合","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:42:03.000Z","uid":264040,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9046ba3b42bb5da7d1f26badbfb6a91ee331ae5c","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係P牌，但唔post我會不得好死<br />\n麻煩大家幫手<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推以下實幹post＋幫手做實事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>7 1 後post</strong></span><br />\n1.我係一個普通香港人 想問一個問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274016</a><br />\n<br />\n2.[文宣] 緊急，如果我地都開記招可唔可行？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277154</a><br />\n<br />\n3.「長期置頂」夢遊後執手尾須知<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276769</a><br />\n<br />\n[長期頂置］入過會議廳既人要報失sim卡同trade電話<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274586</a><br />\n<br />\n4.校園出現白色恐怖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277096</a><br />\n<br />\n5.【緊急】跪求文宣組幫忙救下尋晚被捕嘅貨van義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277740</a><br />\n<br />\n6.我地係咪應該為Zhita搞一場悼念？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277645</a><br />\n<br />\n7.【 突發】《香港己亥宣言》中英日三語登場！盡力為香港定下重光藍圖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276561</a><br />\n<br />\n8.緊急：建制又想玩民調，大家推爆佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276703</a><br />\n<br />\n9.緊急：建制又想玩民調，大家推爆佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276703</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">7 1 前post</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 要求國際特赦組織譴責香港警方濫用暴力，並成立獨立調查團切查事件<br />\n國際特赦組織確認香港警察違反國際人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2. 要求英國政府外交干涉中共認真執行中英聯合聲明，還香港人真自治權，停止干預香港事務<br />\n英國政府稱，有權介入香港事務，保護香港人基本自由，要求中共履行聯合聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258065</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 要求美國通過新版人權民主法案，向中方施壓讓香港2020年真普選行政長官/立法會<br />\n新版人權民主法案 美限港2020前普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253912</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n4. 靠自己，製作宣傳廣告，以現有動畫、警察濫權及蛇齋餅糭片段為藍本，力數港共/建制惡行，係YouTube落廣告<br />\n[最新文宣片] We are Hongkongers! 同時原片德文、法文版本已經上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1257625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1257625</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n5.減低TVB影響力：<br />\n餐廳播TVB時候，嘗試要求轉台<br />\n[長期抗爭] 全港轉台 打擊酒樓茶記TVB壟斷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dajExS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dajExS</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n6. 開咗個tg channel幫大家整合網上有咩可以做!<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=cfdd4042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA</a><br />\n<br />\n7. [無人係議長，人人都是議員] 連登議會之香港未來抗爭藍圖規劃，請大家踴躍發言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8.之前都有好多人發起過, 希望大家繼續一齊響應:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1219467/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1219467/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n9見到tvb可幫手轉台<br />\n【幫手轉台】 入嚟睇睇自己以前部Android機有冇紅外線轉台功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n10. [文化戰]   海外既香港人，中意旅行既人一齊入黎睇睇有咩可以做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276400</a>"},{"pid":"d8b321d6ab8a3be4ccb96b060b9322c8043f89a6","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4eea8d203bf74025fed92f8039b6d2356c603c9b","tid":1277890,"uid":65963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b166542999eaf6fbf808de3477ba49fb77796ced","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f12e3404e48c9c7995fb641a9534333be6d7101f","tid":1277890,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:56.000Z","msg":"ush"},{"pid":"0f5d860e5e4fa422cb466a50444b9017004ba482","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84109e9d9767b6b71778437108e10b8562bf9440","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a5c27726baf265020fa2d72e666489818ae1f78","tid":1277890,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648f7e17b9d2ae56d4d2b29537a824a2035b4f09","tid":1277890,"uid":88431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9e7473cc2eb0fea76ccde75dc80633aa8b40343","tid":1277890,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:08:54.000Z","msg